id: pm-lzzp
title: "CodeFactor/Complexity: zero out the SDK contract-resolution, extension-loader and composition surface"
description: "Behavior-preserving cyclomatic-complexity reduction driving three SDK / extension-platform source files to ZERO CodeFactor Complex Method findings (CC>=18), the next ESLint-suppression baseline reduction after pm-zro7 (which explicitly deferred these). Targets (eslint complexity max 17): src/sdk/cli-contracts/flag-contracts.ts resolveSubcommandFlagContractsForCommand (CC 87 -> table-driven); src/core/extensions/loader.ts parseManifest (CC 75), scanExtensionDirectory (CC 21), registerCommand api closure (CC 22); src/sdk/compose.ts composeExtension activate (CC 43), lintExtensionBlueprint (CC 26). Public SDK surface and contracts full.json stay byte-identical; 100 percent coverage and exported-docstring coverage maintained; eslint-suppressions.json baseline pruned (flag-contracts 1->0, compose 2->0, loader 3->0; total 79->76)."
