acceptance_criteria: "All six functions report CC<=17 under eslint complexity:[error,max:17]; eslint-suppressions.json no longer lists flag-contracts.ts/loader.ts/compose.ts (79->76); contracts full.json byte-identical; pnpm lint + build + 100% test/docstring coverage green; greptile and PR review bots report no outstanding findings."
parent: pm-92if
resolution: "Drove src/sdk/cli-contracts/flag-contracts.ts, src/core/extensions/loader.ts and src/sdk/compose.ts to zero CodeFactor Complex Method findings via behavior-preserving extraction. flag-contracts resolveSubcommandFlagContractsForCommand (CC87) -> two lookup Maps + resolveExtensionLifecycleFlagContracts; loader parseManifest (CC75) -> per-field parsers + parseManifestMetadata aggregator + shared optionalTrimmedString, scanExtensionDirectory (CC21) -> buildUnavailableExtensionScan + collectScannedExtensionWarnings, registerCommand (CC22) -> registerCommandOverride/registerCommandDefinition + resolveCommandDefinitionRunHandler; compose composeExtension.activate (CC43) -> 4 phase helpers (order-preserving), lintExtensionBlueprint (CC26) -> 3 finding collectors. eslint-suppressions.json 79->76. Greptile 5/5 no regressions (1 P2 declined: false positive on untouched deriveExtensionCapabilities — isPresent narrows nullish only, so the typeof object guard is intentional untyped-boundary robustness)."
expected_result: All six functions report CC<=17 (eslint complexity max 17); eslint-suppressions.json drops flag-contracts/loader/compose; full.json byte-identical; pnpm lint + build + 100% test/branch/function/docstring coverage green.
actual_result: All six at CC<=17; suppressions 79->76; full.json byte-identical (md5 unchanged); pnpm lint green; build green; 5259 tests pass at 100/100/100/100; static-quality-gate (incl 100% exported docstrings) green; temp-dir smoke (init/create/list/package init/install/dispatch/explore/health/contracts) all functional.
